Dialogs.Dialog: ▲高嶺＊＊▲.... what's wrong, you seem sleepy.
Hmm... I was reading a novel, and suddenly outside was bright...
You stayed up all night! Are you okay?
What can I do, I'm sleepy... What should I do~.
I forgot something. I have to return early because I have childcare practice today.
Childcare practice... Ah, is it like touching a baby?
Yes. Aika onee-chan care for them▼ And their laughs are so cute♪
Ah~, it can't be. See you later?
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ would make me happy even if I wasn't a child）
It seems that there will be an English class and a surprise test soon.
Well... Do you like them, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Yes, you can know your weaknesses, right? I like to overcome them one by one. I'm happy that way.
This good weather makes me want to skip classes...
What are you trying to do?
I haven't done anything! I just said I wanted to do it!
Hmm, I thought you wanted me to come with you... Don't joke around, okay?
Do you like to eat food in the cafeteria?
I wonder if I should look into it.
A school meal? I don't think ▲高嶺＊＊▲ needs to do that.
Is that so... It's fine then. If you say so.
Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing here?
...I'm worried about the growth of potatoes in the school.
Eh!? ▲高嶺＊＊▲, I didn't know you liked them so much!
...Then I won't be separated from them even if they're harvested. See you later?
（Ha~h... To carry such heavy materials by myself... Sensei is too rough）
Were you surprised? Lend me half of it, please?
Haha, that's right. Well then, thanks for your help.
Would you like to have more calligraphy lessons?
Calligraphy... Well, many people may be happy. It's easy.
Geez. Don't try to skip, okay?
On the other hand, I feel more relaxed. But, it's hard after all...
It seems today we'll have a temporary evacuation drill today, right?
You can't run in the corridors.
Isn't it dangerous if you don't run?
Evacuate as a group, if you'll run, everyone panics. So don't pacic, don't make noise and don't rush.
（Don't panic, make no noise, hurry... it's hard）
Hey, do you know how to stop belly noises?
...You're the only one who thinks like that. What are you thinking? Please.
（Certainly I don't want to tell other guys... but is there any other way?）
▲高嶺＊＊▲... What's wrong, do you have with physical education?
My uniform got a little wet...
Ah, that was it. It does not stands out.
A little embarrassing. I think it's about to dry, so I'll change clothes soon.
（So ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is embarrassed being like this...）
Nothing! I hope it dries quickly!
I want arrive to school by bicycle.
Sounds nice... On a bicycle with you...
Going on a bicycle together ... should we use a two- seater?
Emm...No! Two-seaters are forbidden by school rules, and besides, it's against the rules...
Hey~, did you bring you umbrella to school?
Me? I'm not bringing it, it's a bother.
No, if you don't have one, that's fine. Don't worry, okay?
（What's so bad about not having an umbrella?）
Some class has cooking practice. This smell is...
Hey, is it bad if you bring it in a lunch box and eat it in classroom?
Curry? I don't like the smell... Wouldn't be nice to eat it cold?
...A curry that is delicious even when cold. Hmmm...
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ has such a learning spirit...）
Mmm, if you have a textbook in Japanese, would you lend it to me? I forgot mine...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you forget it? It's rare, but I will.
I may have done graffiti on various pictures, so forgive me.
...Geez, you can't do that. As punishment, I will score the graffiti.
Yes. A lot. I'm going to fall asleep.
The bakery car that was running outside was amazing.
I would be worried if I'm told to say "fresh delicious melon bread".
▲高嶺＊＊▲, don't you want to buy some?
If I go to buy it, would you eat some?
（The next lesson is self- study... Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲?）
That's... I learned the lesson by myself. I have something to ask.
I wonder if I have to resist until the next class.
（I'm lucky! I thought I had to wait...）
It seems they are gathering recipes at the student cafeteria.
He~h. Why don't you apply, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
...Really? You want me to give my seasoning to other people?
Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing?
▲主人公＊▲. I guided a female exchange student to the gym. She was new and doesn't know the place.
In English. I can do a bit of basic conversation.
It was just a little bit, don't see me with those glittering eyes, okay? Right?
▲高嶺＊＊▲.... What's wrong? You have a depressed look.
I got a cooking practice before this...
...It was a practice of how to handle fish.
Yes... but I'll do my best!
（I hate that I can't support you!）
Ah~, sorry. I decided to play table tennis in PE...
But I was so thrilled... I can't beat the members of the table tennis club.
（Well, let's go back to the classroom...）
Ouch... Ah,▲高嶺＊＊▲? Are you okay?
Sorry, I'm in a hurry... I'm sorry, but I'm late... See you.
（That's unusual... She's going to the bathroom?）
...I'm not going to the bathroom, okay?
（The sound of a piano... Maybe it's▲高嶺＊＊▲?）
...Huh? Wasn't you playing the piano,▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Piano? Ah, really. It's a shame, I missed it.
I thought so! ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is even better!
I'm fine at it. Then, shall we go back to the classroom?
Why? I wanted to hear a little more...
No... If you want to listen, ask me later okay? Now, let's go.
Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲.... What are you looking at?
Yes... There's a blackboard eraser on the roof of the bike shed.
Did someone drop it when they were busy?
Maybe? But cleaning with my hands is hard, isn't it?
But it looks fun. Maybe I should try it on my day shift♪
Huh.▲高嶺＊＊▲, what are you doing?
▲主人公＊▲. I'm thinking of going back to the library to return the book... But I'll do it later.
That's because I met you... I'm kidding▼
▲高嶺＊＊▲, is the book you borrowed a love story?
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Do you have any sweets? I'm hungry.
I don't have any because it violates the school rules.
And... because I ate too much at lunch... and sweets. See ya.
（Are you overeating? You don't have to worry about it）
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Is it possible to communicate with UFOs like this?
Geez, what are you talking about.
Ah,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you return a book?
No. I came to borrow one. Emm...
Trying to make your boyfriend crazy▼ Something like that?
Shh. I'm sorry, it was a joke!
▲主人公＊▲. can you lend me a hand?
You push acupuncture points to improve concentration, right? Hmm... Hmm~.
I wonder. Tell me if it works, okay? See ya.
（If I say it works, will you do it again?）
▲主人公＊▲. Are you having a good time? Why don't we go shopping together?
It's okay, but... don't buy anything heavy, okay?
No. I just wanted to go with you. Can't I?
（This kind of thing is like a date）
However, I was thinking about stopping.
Just like that? Is that okay?
You can't get good results even if you're interrupted. Did you change your mind?
Geez.... Don't look at me next time, call me before I yawn, okay?
（Huh, it's▲高嶺＊＊▲... What are you singing?）
▲主人公＊▲. How long have you've been there?
That's good... Then you couldn't hear me, right?
Why the chime went off at this time... Ah, it's▲高嶺＊＊▲. You're still in a break, right?
There are things like that... Ha~a! No way――.
...I'm kidding. You like that kind of stories, right?
Do you know what song was last played on the lunch broadcast? Missed the song's name...
The last one is a visual type song? He~e, I'm also interested in that.
The melody was beautiful, so it would be fun to arrange it on the piano.
I see. I'm sorry, I don't remember the name.
No, it's okay. I will try to do the score if I remember it. Thank you.
...Emm, right? It was a letter from a friend. I was thinking of replying.
Ah, girls often do this in class... You don't have to hide it.
It's a secret between girls, so it's better not to speak with it. Right?
（I'm also worried about it's contents...▲高嶺＊＊▲）
▲高嶺＊＊▲.Hmm? Is there something in your mouth?
Hmm... I got a candy. I always refuse them...
I see, I thought that was forbidden.
I was told it was okay because it was throat candy ...don't you think so?
Don't say probably. Is that okay?
Whassup. They're replacing the vending machine in the sales department. What do you think they'll put next?
That's right... What do you think▲高嶺＊＊▲?
This time, I'd like a super- rich milk tea with 5 times the amount of tea leaves▼
Then I would like an oden drink!
That's just dashi stock... I hope it goes in♪
Why don't they replace the cleaning tools?
Isn't it good if they are old?
It's not that... If the tool is in better condition, it will be more efficient.
Hmm... I feel it's going to be difficult.
I hope we could have fun together...
It's embarrassing... are you in too?
Eh...Emm... ▲高嶺＊＊▲ if you say so!
Thank you. But I'll get angry. I just will take on your feelings▼
（Well, time to go back to the classroom...）
This is a Kakkun knee attack.
Emm~... Why? I said that loud!
In the next national language contest, the sensei nominated me to read. So, I'm a little nervous.
Ah~... I can understand that. Is that your case, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Only in such cases, I do. I usually don't feel like this.
No. I want to speak with Miyauchi sensei. She is like my sister and it's easy to talk to her.
I see... Well, if you're not sick, then I'm glad.
Yes, thank you. Then, I'll go now okay?
（What kind of things do they talk about...）
Do you think it's inconve- nient they inspect our belongings?
It'll be awkward to say I'm in trouble.
After this, is our class turn, so I wonder what they'll find there.
It's an amazing wind... I wonder if we can practice.
It feels good to stand upwind, but you'll make a lot of mistakes, so be careful.
Right. I understand that too. It burns!
Huh~,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Wasn't the girls' club running?
I finished early, so I'm taking a break.
He~h, how long have you been running?
Is that your first time? Want to do it together?
（That's not a break... How tough is,▲高嶺＊＊▲）
Looks like today we will do unusual training.
Eh... By the way, is▲高嶺＊＊▲ a demon?
Pinpon. But, start running, okay? I will catch you♪
It was a dark day today.
Still not enough practice? It's tough.
No, that's not it. What I lack is...
Ah, the meeting?... Shall we go?
After practice, let's go to Menler...
...I'm sorry! It was a punishment game... I can't do it Moyoshi-san!
It's dangerous if you don't concentrate, even if you're just swinging, okay?
......It's true. Fufu! Ah~. I didn't mean that...
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ also loses her concentration. Be careful...）
I was asked to get a replacement because the fluorescent lights in the club room were burned out.
Thank you. See you later then?
（Why did you remember that just by looking at me?）
Hey,▲高嶺＊＊▲. There aren't a lot of galleries today?
Is because of the junior high school students tour.
Maybe in the future we will do the same to our juniors!
Isn't it a bit too late for that?
It's not too late. I think!
Hmm~. Good point, let's show them a lot, right?
（Welcome to Towano High School Tennis Club!）
Huh. Somehow, I was the last one.
You have done it, rather than being the last one...
Isn't Suzuki sensei a bit out of it today?
Yes. It looks like his wife is here.
Don't you want to show off in front of the person you love?
▲高嶺＊＊▲... It's bad! Suzuki sensei is looking this way!
The wind is strong... Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Whassup.
If you stand on the windward side, you might hit a magic ball.
There are many people who don't like muscle training, are they?
I usually do muscles I don't use, so I don't enjoy it.
Sometimes I try to do something like an athletic club, my team...
This is an exercise club! When you're done, I'll give you a massage, okay?
Did I come a little too early...
I saw you... so I came to be with you.
Well then, let's start the tennis court maintenance.
Ah, don't rub them! Show them to me, okay?
You might want to go home today without practicing.
Somehow... Why are you so surprised?
But there are times when you feel that way, right? Yes.
...Thank you. Hmm, I'll do my best!
It's raining. How long do you think it'll rain?
Hmm. I think maybe until noon.
Well then, I vote to keep it up until evening.
It's raining. It looks like it'll pour down hard.
I wish we could have a break from school because of heavy rain.
Geez. Then we couldn't go to school together.
Yes. It's hard to care for your hair on a rainy day.
Oh yeah, girls have it hard. I wish I could tell you tomorrow's weather.
Fufu. Isn't that the weather forecast?
Yes, the blue sky is the best.
Very nice weather. It will be a fun day.
It's a little cloudy. I hope it doesn't rain...
The sky is about to start crying. I wonder if it's okay...
It's cloudy now, but it's okay. It'll be fine. Right?
Yes, the good weather didn't last.
It's raining, can you lift your hand?
It's about time for our date.
Yes, I'm looking forward to it.
I'm looking forward to it a lot more.
Don't you forget about it. It's almost our date!
Of course I remember. I'm looking forward to it.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. It's okay. You don't have to run that much.
（It's rare for ▲高嶺＊＊▲ to be late）
Hmm? My clock is behind time!?
Sorry, can you go first? It seems I forgot my pen case...
I can lend one to you. If you go back, you'll be late.
Is that okay? Thank you... Studying with your things may be a new experience.
Haha, please lend me something next time,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I'm fine. I was absorbed in my books and stayed up late last night... I'm a little sleepy.
Ah, that happens some times to me. I miss my sleep time...
I stepped on something... I wonder what it is...
Lemme see... Hmm? This are work gloves.
Huh? Why is it like this... Phew, I was surprised.
I've made a bento. Want to eat some?
Of course. Where should we eat it.
I made a bento box... I hope it's to your liking.
Today is Aika's special love lunch.
I don't have a bento box today...
Then, why don't we go to the school cafeteria? I haven't been with you yet.
That's right. Looks fun for the first time.
Um, today's lunch... why don't we go to the cafeteria?
School food? No problem. We never been there together.
Hey~, why don't we go to the cafeteria for lunch?
School food, huh. I haven't been there with you. Let's go.
Would you like to have a school meal today?
Why don't we try school lunch?
I had a good school meal today.
I understand, I'll do it too.
Thank for the food. It was delicious.
Ah, I'm too full... and I'm getting sleepy.
Geez, you shouldn't sleep in class, okay?
What a feast. It was delicious...
Was it that much? Then I have to remember... Wait, I'll take notes.
Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you making it?
I'm sorry if it doesn't taste good. Don't expect too much.
Oh, I can't lose either. I have to make a more delicious bento.
You won't lose. For me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s bento is the best.
Fufu, really? In that case, it's fine.
I don't want to get wet, I'm glad I had it with me.
▲主人公＊▲.Hey~, do you have an umbrella?
...Ah, you mean it like that! Let's go home sharing the umbrella.
Yes. Do you have an umbrella?
No problem? Fufu, let's go home.
It's a bother, I have to run back home...
Hey~, do you have an umbrella?
No. If I run back home...
No, you'll get a cold if you get wet. I have an umbrella, so come back with me, okay?
Uh, it's raining a lot... well, let's run.
You know, I have sweets. I made them in home economics class.
I don't think it's strange, though.
Do you think it tastes good? I'm a little worried.
How was it? What are your impressions?
I tried to add a hidden flavor, how do you like it?
（Uh... this hidden flavor is truly hidden... Isn't that wrong?）
Maybe it suits your taste... What do you think?
（Uh... This is... Before the taste, it's ...）
I tried to make it fit your mouth, how do you like it?
Huh...▲高嶺＊＊▲!? Did you come to wake me up?
Yes... You were asleep until a while ago.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, your face looks red... What did I do when I was sleeping?）
Ah, I'm sorry. Did I wake you up?
▲高嶺＊＊▲... You woke me up... Did you come to see me?
Emm~... you had a pretty sleeping face.
Are you shy? I was embarrassed to see you too.
How long are you planning to sleep? You'll be late, okay?
（No way,▲高嶺＊＊▲ is on my futon...）
Your sleeping face is so cute▼
（Hmm...▲高嶺＊＊▲? You came to wake me up）
（It's bad, but I want to sleep a little more...）
Geez, this is troublesome... Is it okay to pour some water?
（I heard something scary... Was that a dream?）
（Are you sure... Was it a dream?）
When I saw your sleeping face, I fell asleep. I'm sorry.
Did you sleep next to me?
Hmm...Is that the smell of miso soup...?
Eh...▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you make breakfast?
Yes. I got up early and came to prepare it for you.
Good morning. Shall we eat breakfast together?
Thank you for coming to make it. Isn't troublesome to do this?
It's fine, sit down. You have to eat properly in the morning to cheer up.
（Ah, looks like a newlywed life... It's a dreamy morning!）
It's delicious! I'm glad I have a girlfriend!
I made it in a hurry, so it might not be perfect.
Sorry. The taste is a little off.
Low salt is the basis of good health! This is delicious.
Good morning. I came to make breakfast.
Fufu~. If you're so happy, call me anytime.
Because there's enough, you can eat a lot.
It's really delicious... I want seconds!
I wonder how it tastes... I made it in a hurry.
I'm sorry, it got a little burnt... Can I leave it?
▲主人公＊▲. Are you going home now?
...Hey~, have you decided what to make for dinner? If not, I was wondering if I could make it for you.
▲主人公＊▲. Are you going home now?
Yes,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Let's go home together.
Yes... Have you thought about dinner? If you'd like, I'm thinking about making it.
Oh, wait. Um, have you decided what to eat for dinner? Shall I make it?
You want to make it,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
I see... I'll see you next time.
Really? Then, can we go buy ingredients? A detour... sounds good.
This shop has a wide selection of products.
I like this shop because it's easy to go by.
Shopping at the supermarket together... Fufu♪
Now then... Hey~, what do you want to eat?
Today, I want to eat▲メニュー▲.
Emm~, it may take some time, but... Is it okay?
Well then, let's prepare the ingredients.
Please, feel like you're in home.
I'm going in. The bag was heavy, right? I'll make something soon.
It may be a little messy, but please go in.
I'm worried I don't cleaned up properly.. Well, please go in.
Don't worry about that kind of thing. I'm going in.
By the way, it's the first time I've had someone to cook for me after school.
Really. When I think so... I get a little nervous.
Thank you. I like your room because it calms me down.
Emm~... let's start preparing the food.
Come on, why don't you shake your arms? Fufu♪
Thank you for today. I was happy.
You're welcome. I'm glad you're happy.
Well then, I'll take you home.
No, I'll be fine from here. See you.
Ah, I'm very satisfied today. Thank you.
Suddenly, I just said that today... I'm sorry?
You're always welcome. I'll see you home.
Ah... No need to do that. I'm going home, so take your time... See you.
Thank you for today. I'll ask to come again.
If you say that, want me to come every day?... I'm kidding.
You're welcome! For now, I'll see you home because it's late.
Don't worry too much. I'll come again, right? Bye bye.
You know, I keep a diary. It's pretty fun.
He~h, what are you writing about?
Eh, why. You would normally tell me.
Normally, you don't show what's inside.
